sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>9178/TCP plaintext
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>configurable/TCP plaintext
    participant SM as Servable Manager
    participant MM as Model Manager
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph Executor
    participant LLM as LLM Calculator<br/>OpenVINO GenAI
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Inference (gRPC - TFS/KServe v2)
    Client->>gRPC: PredictRequest / ModelInferRequest<br/>gRPC/9178 plaintext
    gRPC->>OV: Execute inference<br/>(in-process call)
    OV-->>gRPC: Inference result
    gRPC-->>Client: PredictResponse / ModelInferResponse

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading from S3
    SM->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>SM: Model files
    SM->>MM: Register model version
    MM->>OV: Load model into runtime<br/>(in-process call)
    OV-->>MM: Model loaded

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OpenAI Chat Completions (REST, Streaming)
    Client->>REST: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext
    REST->>MP: Route to MediaPipe graph
    MP->>LLM: Execute LLM Calculator
    LLM->>OV: Generate tokens<br/>continuous batching
    OV-->>LLM: Generated tokens
    LLM-->>MP: Token stream
    MP-->>REST: Streamed response
    REST-->>Client: SSE stream response<br/>HTTP plaintext

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: REST Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTP plaintext
    REST->>OV: Execute inference<br/>(in-process call)
    OV-->>REST: Inference result
    REST-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 5: Health & Metrics
    Client->>REST: GET /v2/health/ready
    REST-->>Client: 200 OK (ready)
    Client->>REST: GET /metrics
    REST-->>Client: Prometheus metrics
